name: Nifty Royale X Lushsux ONE DOES NOT SIMPLY SELL AN NFT

metadata.description: One does not simply paint a meme. Well, it turned out kinda true. This painting was a bit of a mission to finish much like the mission to find the one ring. Painted during a lockdown with a nice little curfew attached as a bonus feature to it, I love my hometown. It's becoming more like Mordor every day. Who will step up and win the 1/1 NFT? I can't lend you my axe but I can give you a limited edition to use as a weapon. One does not simply win a Nifty Royale... I bid thee good luck. - Lushsux
metadata.name: ONE DOES NOT SIMPLY SELL AN NFT

attributes.value: Hailing from Australia Lushsux is self proclaimed as the world’s first and therefore best meme artist. Based in Melbourne, he is best known for his large murals that draw on internet meme culture, as well as popular culture more broadly. NFTs created by Lushsux, which often combine his iconic graffiti arts with animations, have proven to be highly valuable collectibles.
